1
00:01:28,039 --> 00:01:29,160
Run away from the wedding?

2
00:01:29,160 --> 00:01:29,880
No.

3
00:01:30,480 --> 00:01:32,440
But you killing someone is even worse.

4
00:01:32,440 --> 00:01:33,570
If I'm not mistaken,

5
00:01:33,840 --> 00:01:35,800
you plan to kill Hu Wenyi at the wedding reception,

6
00:01:35,800 --> 00:01:36,880
and then take your own life.

7
00:01:36,880 --> 00:01:37,280
Right?

8
00:01:37,560 --> 00:01:38,160
I...

9
00:01:40,479 --> 00:01:42,320
You just want to keep your mother safe,

10
00:01:42,320 --> 00:01:44,160
killing Hu Wenyi to end the trouble forever.

11
00:01:44,160 --> 00:01:45,479
But have you ever thought about it?

12
00:01:45,479 --> 00:01:48,200
You are her only close relative left in the Hu family now.

13
00:01:48,200 --> 00:01:49,600
If you leave her too,

14
00:01:49,800 --> 00:01:52,000
wouldn't she be even more heartbroken?

15
00:01:53,080 --> 00:01:54,880
But about escaping the wedding,

16
00:01:55,200 --> 00:01:56,520
we are almost at the Zhang family.

17
00:01:56,520 --> 00:01:58,520
There's no time to worry about that.

18
00:02:14,320 --> 00:02:15,160
Stop!

19
00:02:15,560 --> 00:02:16,520
Stop!

20
00:02:16,960 --> 00:02:17,960
Stop!

21
00:02:19,960 --> 00:02:20,840
Hu Linglong,

22
00:02:21,280 --> 00:02:22,320
what are you doing?

23
00:02:22,320 --> 00:02:25,050
It is inappropriate for a bride to yell like this.

24
00:02:25,440 --> 00:02:26,960
I ate something bad last night.

25
00:02:26,960 --> 00:02:28,600
I need to use the toilet and can't hold it.

26
00:02:28,600 --> 00:02:29,560
If you don't let me go,

27
00:02:29,560 --> 00:02:30,880
I'll do it right here in the sedan.

28
00:02:30,880 --> 00:02:33,400
I'm not the one who will be embarrassed anyway.

29
00:02:33,400 --> 00:02:33,800
You...

30
00:02:36,600 --> 00:02:37,329
Hu Linglong,

31
00:02:37,520 --> 00:02:38,980
don't play tricks with me.

32
00:02:39,520 --> 00:02:41,840
It's a taboo for the bridal sedan to touch the ground during the procession.

33
00:02:41,840 --> 00:02:42,440
Hold it in.

34
00:02:42,600 --> 00:02:44,240
Lift the sedan and keep moving.

35
00:02:44,240 --> 00:02:46,970
The sedan can't touch the ground. Hold it steady.

36
00:02:58,200 --> 00:02:59,000
Hu Linglong!

37
00:02:59,200 --> 00:02:59,930
Go after her!

38
00:03:05,440 --> 00:03:06,280
Why are they like leeches?

39
00:03:06,280 --> 00:03:07,540
I can't shake them off.

40
00:03:07,680 --> 00:03:08,200
Chase her!

41
00:03:08,200 --> 00:03:08,730
Hurry up!

42
00:03:16,360 --> 00:03:17,240
Chase her that way.

43
00:03:17,240 --> 00:03:18,120
Hurry!

44
00:03:27,800 --> 00:03:28,400
Linglong.

45
00:03:30,600 --> 00:03:31,200
Linglong.

46
00:03:31,640 --> 00:03:32,720
Why are you here?

47
00:03:33,960 --> 00:03:34,680
Zhinian.

48
00:03:35,680 --> 00:03:37,079
You shouldn't have come.

49
00:03:39,079 --> 00:03:40,800
I just escaped from the wedding procession.

50
00:03:40,800 --> 00:03:43,200
They are trying to catch me and take me back.

51
00:03:44,880 --> 00:03:45,520
Zhinian,

52
00:03:45,840 --> 00:03:46,970
you should go first.

53
00:03:47,000 --> 00:03:48,200
I don't want to drag you into this.

54
00:03:48,200 --> 00:03:49,329
I won't leave alone.

55
00:03:49,760 --> 00:03:51,490
I came today to take you with me.

56
00:03:51,840 --> 00:03:52,480
Linglong,

57
00:03:52,480 --> 00:03:53,960
we are already married now.

58
00:03:53,960 --> 00:03:56,360
We should go through thick and thin together.

59
00:03:56,360 --> 00:03:57,240
Zhinian.

60
00:03:58,520 --> 00:03:59,520
She's over there.

61
00:03:59,640 --> 00:04:00,480
Catch her quickly!

62
00:04:00,480 --> 00:04:01,400
Get on the bike quickly.

63
00:04:01,400 --> 00:04:02,120
Let's go.

64
00:04:02,600 --> 00:04:04,130
I'm not very good at riding.

65
00:04:04,200 --> 00:04:04,800
Linglong,

66
00:04:05,240 --> 00:04:06,280
you can ride a bicycle now.

67
00:04:06,280 --> 00:04:07,240
Get on quickly.

68
00:04:08,640 --> 00:04:09,680
Qiao Xin,

69
00:04:09,960 --> 00:04:11,560
this bicycle is a rare item.

70
00:04:11,680 --> 00:04:12,960
Ordinary families don't have it.

71
00:04:12,960 --> 00:04:14,620
Where did you learn to ride it?

72
00:04:14,960 --> 00:04:15,440
Hmph,

73
00:04:15,440 --> 00:04:16,120
don't forget,

74
00:04:16,120 --> 00:04:17,160
I am an immortal.

75
00:04:17,519 --> 00:04:18,839
I can naturally master things in your mortal world

76
00:04:18,839 --> 00:04:20,160
without a teacher.

77
00:04:28,360 --> 00:04:29,160
Oh no.

78
00:04:29,160 --> 00:04:30,360
Why at this time?

79
00:04:37,960 --> 00:04:38,920
Ah.

80
00:04:39,159 --> 00:04:41,000
Zhinian.

81
00:04:41,000 --> 00:04:42,120
Linglong, what's wrong?

82
00:04:42,120 --> 00:04:43,400
I don't know how to ride a bicycle.

83
00:04:43,400 --> 00:04:43,680
Ah.

84
00:04:43,680 --> 00:04:44,560
You've ridden so far.

85
00:04:44,560 --> 00:04:44,960
Hey.

86
00:04:44,960 --> 00:04:45,560
Linglong.

87
00:04:45,600 --> 00:04:46,200
Linglong.

88
00:04:46,600 --> 00:04:47,200
Linglong.

89
00:04:47,280 --> 00:04:48,610
Are you okay, Linglong?

90
00:04:54,000 --> 00:04:54,720
Zhinian,

91
00:04:54,880 --> 00:04:56,409
I think I sprained my ankle.

92
00:05:00,120 --> 00:05:01,050
Let me carry you.

93
00:05:16,640 --> 00:05:17,160
Look.

94
00:05:17,440 --> 00:05:18,600
Isn't that the cabin from before?

95
00:05:18,600 --> 00:05:19,440
Yes.

96
00:05:24,160 --> 00:05:24,920
Ouch!

97
00:05:24,920 --> 00:05:25,840
Dad!

98
00:05:26,320 --> 00:05:27,160
Dabao.

99
00:05:27,160 --> 00:05:27,880
Elder.

100
00:05:28,040 --> 00:05:29,160
What happened to you?

101
00:05:29,160 --> 00:05:29,440
I...

102
00:05:29,440 --> 00:05:30,840
I went to catch Linglong,

103
00:05:31,080 --> 00:05:32,520
but she hit me with her bicycle.

104
00:05:32,520 --> 00:05:32,850
Look.

105
00:05:33,280 --> 00:05:33,800
Ouch.

106
00:05:37,120 --> 00:05:38,159
Hu Linglong.

107
00:05:38,960 --> 00:05:41,020
You have no respect for family rules.

108
00:05:41,400 --> 00:05:43,640
You've tainted our family and caused trouble.

109
00:05:43,640 --> 00:05:44,770
Your sins are grave.

110
00:05:45,760 --> 00:05:46,520
If I am

111
00:05:47,320 --> 00:05:49,180
lenient with her again this time,

112
00:05:50,080 --> 00:05:51,040
after I die,

113
00:05:51,880 --> 00:05:54,440
I won't have the face to see our ancestors.

114
00:05:56,480 --> 00:05:57,040
Dabao.

115
00:05:57,040 --> 00:05:57,440
Yes.

116
00:05:58,159 --> 00:06:00,020
Go find your father immediately.

117
00:06:00,400 --> 00:06:01,330
Take Hu Linglong

118
00:06:01,760 --> 00:06:04,420
and escort her to Hu Wenzhong's memorial tablet

119
00:06:04,600 --> 00:06:05,920
to kneel in punishment.

120
00:06:05,920 --> 00:06:07,360
Without my permission,

121
00:06:08,080 --> 00:06:09,610
she is not allowed to get up.

122
00:06:10,080 --> 00:06:11,920
If she disobeys even a bit,

123
00:06:13,160 --> 00:06:14,000
tell her

124
00:06:14,600 --> 00:06:16,520
I'll hold her mother accountable.

125
00:06:16,520 --> 00:06:17,040
Okay.

126
00:06:17,200 --> 00:06:17,930
Understood.

127
00:06:18,280 --> 00:06:19,240
I'll go right now, Elder.

128
00:06:19,240 --> 00:06:19,640
Go.

129
00:06:31,560 --> 00:06:32,640
Oh!

130
00:06:34,280 --> 00:06:34,960
Ah.

131
00:06:44,159 --> 00:06:45,720
This old man

132
00:06:46,400 --> 00:06:47,680
finally believed it.

133
00:06:50,560 --> 00:06:51,400
Oh my.

134
00:06:51,760 --> 00:06:52,920
Hu Linglong,

135
00:06:53,120 --> 00:06:54,380
let's see how you hide.

136
00:06:57,159 --> 00:06:57,800
Mm.

137
00:06:58,320 --> 00:06:59,480
Good tea.

138
00:07:05,880 --> 00:07:06,520
Smell it.

139
00:07:06,520 --> 00:07:07,480
Smells good.

140
00:07:07,480 --> 00:07:08,080
Mm.

141
00:07:21,200 --> 00:07:22,080
Zhinian.

142
00:07:23,160 --> 00:07:25,400
If time could stop at this moment,

143
00:07:26,120 --> 00:07:27,450
how great would that be.

144
00:07:33,680 --> 00:07:35,140
Even if time doesn't stop,

145
00:07:35,560 --> 00:07:36,960
we can still be together.

146
00:07:41,840 --> 00:07:43,880
But we have to go back eventually,

147
00:07:44,880 --> 00:07:46,080
don't we?

148
00:08:05,080 --> 00:08:06,160
What is he...

149
00:08:12,400 --> 00:08:13,460
I'll give it to him.

150
00:08:17,160 --> 00:08:17,640
Here.

151
00:08:24,880 --> 00:08:26,240
What does he mean?

152
00:08:27,160 --> 00:08:28,290
He seems to be saying

153
00:08:28,720 --> 00:08:29,980
that this house is his.

154
00:08:43,960 --> 00:08:44,720
Linglong.

155
00:08:49,920 --> 00:08:51,160
I want to marry you.

156
00:08:55,720 --> 00:08:57,000
Not like last night.

157
00:08:58,480 --> 00:08:59,760
I will follow all the traditional customs,

158
00:08:59,760 --> 00:09:00,890
formally marry you,

159
00:09:01,760 --> 00:09:04,020
and carry you home in a grand sedan chair.

160
00:09:06,880 --> 00:09:07,560
Actually,

161
00:09:08,160 --> 00:09:10,290
I have been hiding something from you.

162
00:09:13,240 --> 00:09:15,970
It's about taking up my post in the Beiyang Fleet.

163
00:09:19,040 --> 00:09:21,300
You've always been smart and observant,

164
00:09:21,640 --> 00:09:23,440
so naturally you could guess it.

165
00:09:25,600 --> 00:09:27,000
Actually, half a month ago,

166
00:09:27,000 --> 00:09:27,680
I already received

167
00:09:27,680 --> 00:09:30,560
the letter from the Beiyang Fleet notifying me to take up my post.

168
00:09:30,560 --> 00:09:33,360
I was originally scheduled to leave in seven days.

169
00:09:39,440 --> 00:09:41,100
If you are willing to marry me,

170
00:09:41,800 --> 00:09:43,000
I can give up the post,

171
00:09:43,160 --> 00:09:44,560
stay in Qimen from now on,

172
00:09:45,360 --> 00:09:46,960
and live a good life with you.

173
00:09:50,440 --> 00:09:51,400
Zhinian,

174
00:09:52,160 --> 00:09:53,520
you shouldn't be here.

175
00:09:54,080 --> 00:09:56,640
You are an exceptional talent and a pillar of the country.

176
00:09:56,640 --> 00:09:57,600
You shouldn't do this for me,

177
00:09:57,600 --> 00:09:59,240
nor for personal romance,

178
00:09:59,960 --> 00:10:01,620
and waste your bright future.

179
00:10:08,760 --> 00:10:11,160
Today, my mother warned me not to regret it.

180
00:10:12,160 --> 00:10:13,640
That was when I realized

181
00:10:15,360 --> 00:10:17,490
what the most important thing is to me,

182
00:10:17,920 --> 00:10:19,920
and who the most precious person is.

183
00:10:23,840 --> 00:10:25,570
It's the things related to you.

184
00:10:26,680 --> 00:10:28,880
It's the person right in front of me now.

185
00:10:32,120 --> 00:10:32,760
Linglong,

186
00:10:33,800 --> 00:10:35,920
I don't need you to give me an answer right away.

187
00:10:35,920 --> 00:10:36,920
No matter when,

188
00:10:38,120 --> 00:10:39,240
I will wait for you.

189
00:11:45,240 --> 00:11:45,840
Linglong.

190
00:11:46,480 --> 00:11:47,010
Let's...

191
00:11:48,120 --> 00:11:49,000
Let's go.

192
00:12:09,640 --> 00:12:10,160
Bad news!

193
00:12:10,160 --> 00:12:11,120
Bad news, Clan Elder!

194
00:12:11,120 --> 00:12:12,040
What is it, Wenyi?

195
00:12:12,040 --> 00:12:13,970
Something terrible has happened.

196
00:12:14,320 --> 00:12:15,920
What about the Zhang family?

197
00:12:18,040 --> 00:12:19,440
Master Zhang is furious.

198
00:12:19,640 --> 00:12:20,960
The Zhang family canceled the engagement!

199
00:12:20,960 --> 00:12:21,840
Canceled the engagement?

200
00:12:21,840 --> 00:12:22,560
Yes.

201
00:12:23,480 --> 00:12:25,320
Then our tea orders...

202
00:12:26,240 --> 00:12:28,040
The tea orders they promised...

203
00:12:28,120 --> 00:12:29,280
Naturally, they are...

204
00:12:29,280 --> 00:12:30,640
canceled too.

205
00:12:34,560 --> 00:12:35,440
Wenyi!

206
00:12:35,720 --> 00:12:37,320
What are you standing there for?

207
00:12:37,320 --> 00:12:39,160
Hurry and bring her back!

208
00:12:39,840 --> 00:12:40,770
Yes, Clan Elder.

209
00:12:54,760 --> 00:12:55,890
Linglong. Zhinian.

210
00:13:02,240 --> 00:13:03,040
Benefactors.

211
00:13:06,240 --> 00:13:06,800
Wow.

212
00:13:07,200 --> 00:13:08,920
You two look so beautiful today.

213
00:13:08,920 --> 00:13:10,580
Come, let me pour you some tea.

214
00:13:18,280 --> 00:13:19,640
Extra! Extra!

215
00:13:19,640 --> 00:13:21,520
Japan has attacked without declaring war!

216
00:13:21,520 --> 00:13:22,240
Paperboy!

217
00:13:22,840 --> 00:13:23,440
Sir.

218
00:13:23,440 --> 00:13:24,680
Would you like a newspaper?

219
00:13:24,680 --> 00:13:25,480
Give me a copy.

220
00:13:30,040 --> 00:13:31,440
Extra! Extra!

221
00:13:31,560 --> 00:13:33,960
Japan has attacked without declaring war!

222
00:13:38,240 --> 00:13:38,960
Zhinian,

223
00:13:39,120 --> 00:13:39,920
what's wrong?

224
00:13:40,160 --> 00:13:41,800
Japan has attacked without declaring war.

225
00:13:41,800 --> 00:13:44,130
They ambushed our troop transport ships.

226
00:13:47,160 --> 00:13:48,120
Can we win?

227
00:13:52,000 --> 00:13:52,600
Yes.

228
00:13:54,160 --> 00:13:55,200
Xu Zhinian.
